**Assassin** | Townsfolk Killing
__Basics__
After night 1, the Assassin may choose one player to attack during the night.
__Details__
The Assassin has a total of 3 knives they can use throughout a game to attack. The Assassinâ€™s attack is an end-night ability.

__Simplified__
After night 1, the Assassin may choose one player to attack during the night. They may only attack 3 times throughout the game.

__Formalized__
End Night: Attack @Selection [Temporal: Night 2+, Quantity: 3]

__Card__
The Assassin has three knives and isn't afraid to leave them in people's backs.
